headline: Jacobs to Lead Terminal Modernization at Ohio's Busiest Airport
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected to lead program and construction management services for phase one of a $1.6 billion modernization of Cleveland Hopkins International Airport (CLE).
